author: ETA PRIME
description:
In this video, we take a first look at the all-new 2025 ASUS ROG NUC 15 and put it through its paces. This is one of the most powerful mini PCs on the market—compact at under 3L, configurable up to an RTX 5090, and built for serious performance. Our test unit features an Intel Core Ultra 9 275HX paired with an NVIDIA GeForce RTX 5070 Ti, and it absolutely flies, chewing through modern games and creator workloads. Let’s see just how far this tiny beast can go!
